name: ExtensionManufacturedItemDefinition_Property
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.ManufacturedItemDefinition.property` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`ManufacturedItemDefinition.property` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `ManufacturedItemDefinition.property` is not mapped to FHIR R4, since FHIR R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition` is not mapped.
